_sText:
This map is made for 28 players. There is a buy zone at the spawns for each team. At each spawn there are 2 towers that can be acessed by running to the top of the spawn on climbing a ladder. 

This map is made entirely of the reflectivity texture making it easy to see both teams no matter where they go.

I tested the map with bots and it worked out very nicely, that's also when I got my screen shots (see pics of map).

This map is fairly strategic, but is still a fast map good for gun game.
